The Norwegian Institute for Public Health has coordinated a study on the development of the motor of children whose mothers have been treated with SSRI, analysing the data of 51 404 children in the Norwegian mother and child cohort study, examining the effects of using SSRI for the development of the motor capacity at the age of 3.
